'''Alberto da Costa e Silva''' (born 12 May 1931, in [[São Paulo]]) is a Brazilian [[historian]], [[poet]] and former [[diplomat]]. He won the 2014 [[Camões Prize]].<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.publico.pt/culturaipsilon/noticia/o-premio-camoes-2014-vai-este-ano-para-1638103|title= O Prémio Camões 2014 é o brasileiro Alberto da Costa e Silva|author=  Cláudia Carvalho|date= 30 May 2014|accessdate= 9 July 2014|work= ''[[Público (Portugal)|Público]]''|language= Portuguese}}</ref><ref name="academia">{{cite web |url= http://www.academia.org.br/abl/cgi/cgilua.exe/sys/start.htm?infoid=48&sid=144|title= Alberto da Costa e Silva Biografia|accessdate= 9 July 2014|work= www.academia.org.br|publisher= [[Academia Brasileira de Letras]]|language= Portuguese}}</ref>

==Diplomacy==
He was [[ambassador]] of [[Brazil]] in [[Portugal]] from 1986 to 1990, in [[Colombia]] from 1990 to 1993 and in [[Paraguay]] from 1993 to 1995.<ref name="academia"/>

